Class wgResource

java.lang.Object
workloadgenerator.wgResource
public class wgResource extends Object
Represents a single resource entry used by the workload generator.

A wgResource contains a reference to its parent wgResources group, an integer ID and header strings used for export. The generator assigns sequential IDs when resources are added to a group.
